                    <li>App activity tracking with timeline lane showing app usage</li>
                    <li>Meetings lane in calendar timeline view</li>
                    <li>Date picker filter in transcription history</li>
                    <li>Model download progress bar in onboarding</li>
                    <li>Play/stop toggle in transcription history</li>
