        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1.0</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 16 Mar 2026 20:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.1.0</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>What's New in 1.1.0</h3>
                <h4>Security</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Removed authentication token from app bundle</li>
                    <li>Moved update distribution to public release channel</li>
                    <li>Removed explicit sandbox opt-out from entitlements</li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Bundle Identity</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Updated bundle identifier to proper reverse-DNS format</li>
                    <li>Automatic migration of Keychain items, UserDefaults, and login items from previous versions</li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Menu Bar App</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Shout now runs as a menu-bar-only app by default</li>
                    <li>Launch at login now uses modern macOS login items (System Settings &gt; Login Items)</li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Automation</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>New shout:// URL scheme — control Shout from Terminal, scripts, or other apps</li>
                    <li>App Intents for Shortcuts — start/stop recording and check status from Shortcuts.app or Siri</li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Clipboard</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Transcription paste now preserves your clipboard — original contents are restored after pasting</li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Compatibility</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Now supports macOS 14 Sonoma and later</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
