        <item>
            <title>Version 1.0.9</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2026 22:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.0.9</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.9</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>What's New in 1.0.9</h3>
                <h4>Smarter Audio Device Recovery</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Smart device fallback with priority ordering — saved device, system default, built-in mic, then other devices</li>
                    <li>Detects Bluetooth disconnections that don't change the default device</li>
                    <li>Device health checks prevent fallback to unhealthy devices</li>
                    <li>Recovery now escalates instead of giving up after 3 attempts</li>
                    <li>CoreAudio negotiation moved off main thread to prevent UI freezes</li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Onboarding &amp; Licensing</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Language selection and model download steps in onboarding</li>
                    <li>Paywall view with trial badge</li>
                    <li>Privacy toggle switches consistently aligned</li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Bug Fixes</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed audio engine -10877 errors on device switch</li>
                    <li>Fixed Swift concurrency warnings and deprecated API usage</li>
                    <li>UI improvements to menu bar, notification cards, and settings</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <enclosure
                url="https://github.com/messisawesome10/shout-releases/releases/download/v1.0.9/Shout-1.0.9.zip"
